{"tid":2002743,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"新香港人掃新盤借爆廠 業主員工：老闆情緒好低落","createTime":"2020-05-05T11:07:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T11:15:18.000Z","uid":12609,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e9e0bfc5d5e0dac45a0b41cb7e2c2c1560fb228b","tid":2002743,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T11:07:02.000Z","msg":"美國減息，負利率年代再度降臨，逼使資金由存款轉向實物投資，加上香港樓市剛性需求大，理論上本港樓價企穩。不過近日市場上，竟湧現了不少劈價銀主盤，而大部份都是2017年落成的新盤，如南昌匯璽及北角柏蔚山等。本刊追蹤這些銀主盤的業主，發現他們都是新香港人，而且不止買入一兩個單位，而是掃貨形式購入，更用來借銀行、再借爆財仔「撳錢」。最終資金周轉不靈..............(詳情去壹週睇)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_738747_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_738747_0&d=gd6RRKTkNwPNcypoJW5ktc5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=8536471e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_738747_0&h=857a6279\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_738747_0</a>"},{"pid":"19d430380e3b65dfea5d64e344c9ae62e47e7e30","tid":2002743,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T11:15:18.000Z","msg":"借位回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我係香港人Tee&rdquo;設計師的憤怒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1281000\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1281000</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MJxYJM5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMJxYJM5.png&h=136ff66a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ys2q0q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ys2q0q.png&h=570971cb&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}